data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! This stunning split foyer residence boasts 1904 square feet of beautifully designed living space, offering the perfect blend of comfort, style, and eco-friendly features. Situated on a spacious .99 acre lot, this property provides ample room for outdoor activities and relaxation. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a perfect space for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen features brand new appliances and a convenient pantry, ensuring that meal preparation is both efficient and enjoyable. This home offers three generous bedrooms, providing plenty of space. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet, offering both luxury and practicality. With three well-appointed bathrooms in total, there's no need to worry about morning rush hours. Additionally, this property boasts a bonus room, which can be customized to suit your needs - whether it be a home office, playroom, or a cozy den for relaxation. The thoughtful layout of this home ensures that there's a space for every purpose.
One of the standout features of this home is its commitment to energy efficiency. Green home improvements, including energy-efficient insulation and a solar fan, not only contribute to a reduced carbon footprint but also result in substantial cost savings on energy bills. Embrace sustainable living while enjoying the comfort of your new home. Conveniently located close to the interstate, this home offers easy access to nearby amenities. Whether you're commuting to work or exploring the local area, you'll appreciate the prime location of this residence. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home - schedule a viewing today and experience the magic for yourself! Boundary lines shown in video are approximate not exact. All information is deemed reliable, but should be verified by buyers/buyers' agent
